Day1:
React is an open source javascript libaray for creating the user interfaces.
Used for handling the view layer of our application
It allows us to create large web applications that can change data without reloading the webpage
React is created and maintained by the facebook 
It is simple and it uses the special syntax called JSX(javascript XML) which allows us to mix both HTML with JS
And if we wants to create the applications for the mobiles, we have to react native(Mobile app development)
React is following component based architecture, which means the application can be broken down into muliple small components and components allow reuse of the code
